                <h2 style="color: white;">1. Above The Line
                </h2>
                
                <br>
                <h3 style="color: white;">Above the line in film production refers to the costs of making <br> a movie associated with the major creative talent, including the <br> director, actors, writers, and producers. Films with special effects<br> will also have a greater number of above the line personnel and <br>costs than films without them.</h3>
               
