                <h2 style="color: white;">2. Below The Line
                </h2>
                
                <br>
                <h3 style="color: white;">Below the line (BTL) refers to any production costs not included in the above-the-line portion of the budget. It also refers to technical crew roles: workers who do not provide input, guidance, creative development, or leadership on the project.</h3>
               
            </div>
        </div>
