                <h3 style="color: white;">The post-production budget includes expenses related to editing, sound design, and visual effects. The innovative use of visual effects in "The Matrix" (1999) accounted for a large part of its post-production budget, significantly contributing to the film's unique visual aesthetic and success..</h3>
               
